A Mac OS X Screen saver based on the work of the following reddit post:

http://www.reddit.com/r/programming/comments/8zxgy/i_love_clocks_and_javascript_and_canvas_so_i_made/

You can watch your seconds (and minutes and hours) slowly drain away. Depressing and fun, at the same time!

Source code by http://www.reddit.com/user/misterjoker

Mac OS X port by frederik at pandora dot be.
